{"tid":2094893,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"健康劈佛.....減肥餐","createTime":"2020-07-05T04:55:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-05T12:28:36.000Z","uid":228002,"like":5,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"bee6e19ac9b24099b82226da177af690bf871c87","tid":2094893,"uid":228002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T04:55:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ibmCWjW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FibmCWjW.png&h=5036dd66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n焗紅椒粒百里香嫩蛋配黃椒杯<br />\n+130g西蘭花<br />\n+80g青瓜<br />\n+1隻奇異金果<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cacdb43f61a84297ec69d2ffdac13308fa78655e","tid":2094893,"uid":202883,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T07:53:41.000Z","msg":"想問巴打好耐<br />\n點樣將奇異果原個攞出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4135dc3e69e22af3d4defe74da95b52e6dfa1602","tid":2094893,"uid":228002,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T08:26:58.000Z","msg":"先將奇異果切開一半<br />\n然後攞個匙羹沿着邊位插落去<br />\n然後慢慢轉一個圈將佢皮肉分離<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係要啲時間 不過口爆個下真係好撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果你隻奇異果夠熟<br />\n好容易就會整到出嚟<br />\n但如果你隻奇異果唔算太熟<br />\n最好就慢慢嚟如果唔係會插穿啲皮"},{"pid":"5eb09ec7d3b05957648ef44730708d63fc6d0742","tid":2094893,"uid":242779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T08:28:57.000Z","msg":"不如扣埋隻蛋食素算啦"},{"pid":"94c03abb036279d563c554e34f97beffea5e3963","tid":2094893,"uid":56716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T08:34:26.000Z","msg":"正，但鍾意牛油果同三文魚多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01c39e05c164960b6abda812e56593e4889e82df","tid":2094893,"uid":51753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T08:39:17.